<h3></h3>
<h3>Participate</h3>
<p>Participate in a competitive sporting event as a team player. Information meetings and try out dates are posted on each sport's page. Remember - you must attend at least one information meeting to participate. Please note participation fees and practice time/game commitments.</p>
<h3>Coach</h3>
<p>Build your résumé and gain invaluable leadership qualities by getting involved in competitive sports leadership. Once you have participated as a team player, you are eligible to apply for a coaching position. Please note that some sports do not permit coaches to play as a participant. Assistant coaches are allowed to play in every sport.</p>
